SELECT SUM(DbT5913ChosainJoho."chosaKanoNinzuPerMonth") FROM rgdb."DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho" AS DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho INNER JOIN rgdb."DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster" AS DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster ON DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho."shichosonCode" = DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster."shichosonCode" INNER JOIN rgdb."DbT5913ChosainJoho" AS DbT5913ChosainJoho ON DbT5913ChosainJoho."shichosonCode" = DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster."shichosonCode" AND DbT5913ChosainJoho."ninteiChosaItakusakiCode" = DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho."ninteichosaItakusakiCode" AND DbT5913ChosainJoho."chikuCode" = #{地区コード} AND DbT5913ChosainJoho."jokyoFlag" = TRUE WHERE DbT7051KoseiShichosonMaster."shoKisaiHokenshaNo" = #{保険者番号} AND DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho."autoWaritsukeFlag" = TRUE AND DbT5910NinteichosaItakusakiJoho."jokyoFlag" = TRUE
